{"tid":2013261,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美聯儲開始購買公司債ETF","createTime":"2020-05-12T07:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T08:41:38.000Z","uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5202f67b560e79e6fea2c9a2c0774f11290e319d","tid":2013261,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/4476221/l/e22924792eb5377506e72baf80f538b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F4476221%2Fl%2Fe22924792eb5377506e72baf80f538b7.jpg&h=7ca95586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據《彭博社》報導，在疫情爆發後的大規模救市後，近日聯準會開始有關鍵動作，聯準會紐約分行周一 (11 日) 表示，聯準會將於今日晚間 (12 日) 開始介入公司債市場，將會針對相關<span style=\"color: red;\">追蹤公司債的 ETF 的次級市場進行購買</span>。<br />\n<br />\n聯準會紐約分行公告表示，這此購買計畫以美國投資級公司債券為優先購買，其次才是美國高收益公司債券，並會針對 ETF 成分股、管理方式以及 ETF 持有的債務數量來做購買審核依據。<br />\n<br />\n此消息最早於 3 月首次宣布，相關救市消息短期間給予市場強心針，也漸漸穩定了當時出現流動性問題的債市以及恐慌性拋售的股市。聯準會於報告中提到，針對一級市場購買，也就是直接購買企業發行的公司債的計劃將於不久將來啟動。<br />\n<br />\n此消息資金來源源自於美國國會在 3 月份通過的超過 2 兆美元的經濟救助計劃中，其中 4540 億美元為聯準會可用資金規模，而這此針對公司債 ETF 購買為首個運用此資金的計畫。<br />\n<br />\n目前聯準會實施的 9 項緊急貸款計劃中，包括企業信貸，以緩解疫情對美國經濟的衝擊並維持流動性正常，此次救市為 1950 年代以來，<span style=\"color: red;\">首次涉及企業債務，意味著央行對金融市場干預力道已逐漸增加</span>。"},{"pid":"23e2f13b2104f8b59454ab07a286fd9474da8fc3","tid":2013261,"uid":44884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:37:02.000Z","msg":"pff?"},{"pid":"891b1f2c377d13a6002687afc8ffab4c9ed326fb","tid":2013261,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23e2f13b2104f8b59454ab07a286fd9474da8fc3","tid":2013261,"uid":44884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:37:02.000Z","msg":"pff?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:37:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-05-12/fed-says-it-will-begin-purchasing-corporate-debt-etfs-on-tuesday\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-05-12%2Ffed-says-it-will-begin-purchasing-corporate-debt-etfs-on-tuesday&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=b6528e8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-05-12/fed-says-it-will-begin-purchasing-corporate-debt-etfs-on-tuesday</a>"},{"pid":"0adf54f96f39703e1ff540172c2fff92b04b4f7a","tid":2013261,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:38:32.000Z","msg":"升災"},{"pid":"35f0ca8d8da444367d65d3fd3a60706b31942c55","tid":2013261,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:40:16.000Z","msg":"快D直接買股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba15566fadd69563f6acde07aee03d03d993ded","tid":2013261,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:00:26.000Z","msg":"白痴一問<br />\n<br />\n將來企業還債俾聯儲局後，會唔會銷毀返堆美金"},{"pid":"8a1e9730bb02af391b33cb57c4db7cd43345d262","tid":2013261,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bba15566fadd69563f6acde07aee03d03d993ded","tid":2013261,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:00:26.000Z","msg":"白痴一問<br />\n<br />\n將來企業還債俾聯儲局後，會唔會銷毀返堆美金"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:22:07.000Z","msg":"緊係唔會<br />\n無限qe根本無縮表schedule"},{"pid":"14c6b43e969f84e895c01648170c752ab69db562","tid":2013261,"uid":177039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"直接大手買期貨推高指數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fb3bb919d448a4aefaa123505b83acbb4d31da","tid":2013261,"uid":36543,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mDw35wP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmDw35wP.jpg&h=bdc9e157&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"772307fbfeaca0d49098456cd75edd517b382cbe","tid":20132